message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CV" (Computer Vision) as it deals with visual question answering using deep learning frameworks. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it also involves natural language processing, "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as deep learning is a subfield of AI, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as the paper discusses the use of LSTM networks and convolutional neural networks, and "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as the task involves retrieving information from an image and a question.
